				<div id="article-header">
	<h1 id="article-headline">Patients die or suffer harm in 10% of NHS safety mishaps</h1>
	
	<div id="article-meta">
	<ul>
	<li class="article-meta-author">by <a class='i-author' href='http://www.walesonline.co.uk/authors/madeleine-brindley/'>Madeleine Brindley</a>, WalesOnline</li>
	
	<li class="article-meta-date"><a class="i-date" href="http://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/wales-news/2012/01/12/" title="Find all articles published on Jan 12 2012 to the Wales News section">Jan 12 2012</a></li>
	
	</ul>
	</div><!-- #article-meta -->
	
